## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all current applications of gaming technology in the pharmaceutical industry. The rapid pace of technological advancement means that new developments may have emerged since the publication of the sources used. Additionally, the scope of the search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant research published in other languages.